This program holds the details of multiple students, their courses, attendance of that course, their faculty, marks, personal details, events participated in, awards and achievements, initially read from a text file. 

HOW TO USE:

Run the Driver class.
It gives options, if you are a student or a teacher.
The teacher has rights to both see and edit the information of the student, while student can only see his information. 
If faculty chooses to edit, he gets to choose the student, which course, which information about it the faculty wants to change.

All the changes are finally stored in an object file.

 


